{"nodes": [{"id": "devlog_phase0", "label": "Development Log \u2014 Phase 0: Foundation", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L9-L46", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-17", "author": "onesixeight", "contributor": null}, {"id": "devlog_phase1a", "label": "Development Log \u2014 Phase 1a: Auth Backend", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L50-L87", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-18", "author": "onesixeight", "contributor": null}, {"id": "devlog_phase1b", "label": "Development Log \u2014 Phase 1b: Auth Frontend", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L90-L122", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-19", "author": "onesixeight", "contributor": null}, {"id": "phase0_foundation", "label": "Phase 0: Foundation (COMPLETE)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L9-L46", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-17", "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Built pnpm+Turborepo monorepo, apps/api (NestJS 11) + apps/web (Next.js 16) skeletons, packages/shared Zod SSoT, docker-compose (postgres:16+redis:7), GitHub Actions CI, root ESLint gate. Adopted current stable majors via ADR 0001 rather than the plan's 2024-era pins because shipping mid-2026 on stale majors would be a reviewer red flag and force painful mid-project upgrades."}, {"id": "phase1a_auth_backend", "label": "Phase 1a: Auth Backend (COMPLETE)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L50-L87", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-18", "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Implemented register/login/refresh/logout/me + admin-probe against real Postgres+Redis. Single 0001_init migration with all 12 domain models to reduce migration churn across later phases. TokenService is the only place that signs/verifies JWT and touches the Redis denylist, so there is a single verify source."}, {"id": "phase1b_auth_frontend", "label": "Phase 1b: Auth Frontend (COMPLETE)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L90-L122", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-19", "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Built login/register pages (RHF+Zod shared schemas), Zustand in-memory token store, TanStack Query mutations + silent refresh on 401, (dashboard) Server Component guard. UI primitives hand-rolled because shadcn/ui init is known-broken on Tailwind v4 (spec \u00a77/\u00a710)."}, {"id": "access_token_stateless", "label": "Access-token statelessness preserved", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L66-L67", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-18", "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "TokenService.verify skips the Redis denylist for typ:access. An access denylist would negate stateless verification (spec \u00a74); the short access TTL (default 15m) is the accepted exposure window for a stolen access token."}, {"id": "logout_idempotency", "label": "Logout is idempotent", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L64-L65", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-18", "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Invalid/missing refresh on logout returns 200 {success:true} as a no-op so flaky client retries are harmless. This is a deliberate, documented deviation from spec \u00a74's '401 if no valid refresh' on logout."}, {"id": "dev_proxy_decision", "label": "Dev proxy: /api/* \u2192 API_ORIGIN (default :4000)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L95-L96", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-19", "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Next.js rewrite proxies /api/:path* to ${API_ORIGIN}/:path* so the browser issues same-origin requests and the sameSite=lax refresh cookie is sent/accepted in dev without cross-origin CORS-cookie gymnastics or wildcard-origin-with-credentials rejection. CORS already permits localhost:3000 with credentials:true. Prod cross-origin + sameSite:none;secure deferred to Phase 10."}, {"id": "cookie_path_widen_auth_to_root", "label": "Refresh cookie path widened /auth \u2192 /", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L94", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-19", "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "The (dashboard) Server Component guard must read the refresh cookie at /dashboard via next/headers cookies(), so the cookie cannot be scoped to /auth. Widening to / is safe: it is httpOnly (no JS access) and only /auth/refresh + /auth/logout consume it server-side; the frontend reaches them via the /api same-origin proxy."}, {"id": "server_component_cookie_guard", "label": "(dashboard) Server Component cookie guard", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L106-L107", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-19", "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "The guard checks cookie presence, not validity: presence means 'the browser might have a session' (the access token is in-memory and never reaches the server); validity is re-established client-side via silent refresh. A revoked-but-present cookie falls through the guard, but the dashboard's failed-refresh path redirects to /login."}, {"id": "zod_400_per_route_pipe", "label": "Zod\u2192400 via per-route ZodValidationPipe", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L66", "source_url": null, "captured_at": "2026-06-18", "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Chose per-route ZodValidationPipe (\u2192400 on weak password) instead of the plan's global ZodExceptionFilter. Same spec outcome, co-located with the route it validates."}], "edges": [{"source": "devlog_phase1a", "target": "spec_execution_process", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L5", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "devlog_phase0", "target": "adr0001_tech_stack", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L20", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "devlog_phase1a", "target": "adr0002_refresh_rotation", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L65", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "devlog_phase0", "target": "phase0_foundation", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.9, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L9-L46", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "devlog_phase1a", "target": "phase1a_auth_backend", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.9, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L50-L87", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "devlog_phase1b", "target": "phase1b_auth_frontend", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.9, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L90-L122", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase0_foundation", "target": "adr0001_tech_stack", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L20-L23", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "adr0002_refresh_rotation", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L64-L65", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "refresh_token_rotation", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L58", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "httponly_refresh_cookie", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L61", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "jti_denylist_redis", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.8, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L58", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "token_type_enforcement", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.8, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L58", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "first_admin_bootstrap", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.8, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L59", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "logout_idempotency", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.8, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L65", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "access_token_stateless", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.8, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L67", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "zod_400_per_route_pipe", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.8, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L66", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "critical_path_tests_11", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.9, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L62-L75", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1a_auth_backend", "target": "throttler_on_auth", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.8, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L61", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1b_auth_frontend", "target": "dev_proxy_decision", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.9, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L95", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1b_auth_frontend", "target": "cookie_path_widen_auth_to_root", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.9, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L94", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1b_auth_frontend", "target": "server_component_cookie_guard", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L101-L107", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "phase1b_auth_frontend", "target": "access_token_in_memory", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L105", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "cookie_path_widen_auth_to_root", "target": "server_component_cookie_guard", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L94-L107", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "dev_proxy_decision", "target": "httponly_refresh_cookie", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.8, "source_file": "DEVELOPMENT_LOG.md", "source_location": "L95", "weight": 1.0}], "hyperedges": []}